trans-unit.source: Represents information about a SOAP fault that is specified in a <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultContractAttribute> attribute.
trans-unit.target: Representerer informasjon om et SOAP-feil som er angitt i en <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultContractAttribute>attributtet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultContractAttribute>

trans-unit.source: You can get a collection of FaultContractInfo objects by accessing the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ClientOperation.FaultContractInfos%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.DispatchOperation.FaultContractInfos%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: Du får en samling FaultContractInfo objekter ved å åpne den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ClientOperation.FaultContractInfos%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.DispatchOperation.FaultContractInfos%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Egenskaper.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.DispatchOperation.FaultContractInfos%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ClientOperation.FaultContractInfos%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The FaultContractInfo class exposes the action of the SOAP fault and the detail type that is serialized into the SOAP fault.
trans-unit.target: Klassen FaultContractInfo viser handlingen av SOAP-feil og detalj-type som er serialisert i SOAP-feil.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.FaultContractInfo"></xref> class that uses the specified action and detail type.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.FaultContractInfo"> </xref> klassen som bruker den angitte handling og detalj-typen.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new FaultContractInfo from the `action` and `detail`.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny FaultContractInfo fra den `action` og `detail`.

trans-unit.source: The action of the SOAP fault.
The detail type that is serialized as the SOAP fault detail.
trans-unit.target: Detaljer-type som er serialisert som detaljert for SOAP-feil.

trans-unit.source: Gets the SOAP fault action value.
The type of the object that is serialized as the SOAP fault detail.
trans-unit.target: Typen for objektet som er serialisert som detaljert for SOAP-feil.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> that represents the serialized SOAP fault detail.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>som representerer den serialiserte SOAP feil detaljen.</xref:System.Type>
